description: Some people have such a nice and easy life and they barely know it. These two brothers had very generous parents. They paid their rent and even gave our boys 40 000 for a new car. Neither of them was very smart so I wasn´t surprised to hear that they lost the money at a party. They already paid deposit for the car and now lacked 30 000. The parents would get mad if they found out about their sons stupidity. I was called to solve the situation. These lazy fools had no stable jobs to pay the money back so our discussion turned naughty very soon. If you can´t pay me back the debt, you will have to work it off. A very simple proposition. I brought my big red dildo with me.
title: Debt Dandy 195
